"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Subset analysis of 1016 survivors of sudden death or hemodynamically significant ventricular tachycardia entered into the AVID trial. The hazard ratios for death from any cause with the implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD), compared with amiodarone, were not significantly different for any of the prespecified subgroups.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
